high_descs: Turn to the left and then the right to go around the island. Face the island on the right side.
Pick up the fork from behind the wine bottle.
Carry the fork and turn around to the sink.
Place the fork inside the sink.
Turn around to face the island again.
Pick up the fork from the center of the island.
Carry the fork and turn around to the sink.
Place the fork in the sink, standing straight up.
anns.task_desc: Move two forks to the sink.

high_descs: Go left and then right and then turn right again to face the green table.
Pick the fork that is behind the bottle and to the right of the other fork, up from the table.
Turn around and face the sink behind.
Put the fork in the sink.
Turn around to face the green table behind again.
Pick the other fork up from the table.
Turn around to face the sink again.
Put the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two forks in a sink.
